| /dev/snd/dsp1  |  minor = 3 + 16*1  | aic1(i2s1)  |
| /dev/snd/dsp2  |  minor = 3 + 16*2  | pcm0        |
| /dev/snd/dsp3  |  minor = 3 + 16*3  | pcm1        |
\---------------------------------------------------/

